===Noun===
'''[[ice]] [[cream]]''' (''[[uncountable]] and [[countable]]''; ''plural'' '''[[ice creams]]''')

#(''uncountable'') A [[dessert]] made from [[frozen]] [[sweeten]]ed [[cream]] or a similar substance, usually [[flavour]]ed.
#(''countable'') A snack consisting of ice cream (1) in a wafer cone.

====Synonyms====
*(''dessert'') [[iced cream]] (''dated'')
*(''in a wafer cone''): [[cone]], [[cornet]], [[ice cream cone]], [[ice-cream cornet]]

